room_title: Escape room "Vampire Hunter Room" by Clue Carré in New Orleans
review: We had a great time. We were grouped up with a sweet couple who were very smart and we all worked very well together. We would all love to go back and check out the other rooms. The vampire won in the end, but we will get him next time! Be sure to leave very early, they run on a tight schedule, which is understandable, and you don't want to miss your adventure!

room_title: Escape room "Vampire Hunter Room" by Clue Carré in New Orleans
review: So much fun!! Our group can't wait to try another room for a new experience!!

room_title: Escape room "Vampire Hunter Room" by Clue Carré in New Orleans
review: I will definitely be back. Excellent time!! Everyone in our party loved it and wants to go back! Love a good challenge!! Highly recommend!!!

room_title: Escape room "Vampire Hunter Room" by Clue Carré in New Orleans
review: If you're ever in New Orleans- this is definitely a must! We will definitely be back soon to the do the other room. We needed a good amount of help on escaping, but we finally did! Would recommend to anyone. Can't wait until they open the more rooms so we can go back for more!

room_title: Escape room "Vampire Hunter Room" by Clue Carré in New Orleans
review: My friends and I had a blast trying to escape the haunted swamp room! Will definitely be going again. I would recommend this to anybody that enjoys a challenging puzzle. A must go.
